title: Reduce the threshold for receiving liquidity provider rewards from 5% to a lower %
body: In reference to https://forums.dydx.community/proposal/discussion/1805-reduce-market-maker-incentives/,  what should be the volume threshold % for MMs to qualify to receive liquidity provider rewards on dYdX?
